Grandview Elementary students had another sucessful year in competing in the Invention Convention. Students in grades 2-5 competed at Yough Intermediate School on December 13, 2018. The following Grandview Elementary students received awards:
Second grade - Lincoln Tittle, 3rd Place;
Third grade - Jenna Vargulish, 5th Place;
Fourth grade- Max Doherty, 1st Place; Liam McMahen, 5th Place; Molly McNeal, Honorable Mention;
Fifth grade - John Kerin, 1st Place.

